3827,IssuesEvent,2015-02-13 15:28:10+00:00,5888353,spotify/luigi,991878,alsa,251374,spotify,opened,Negative task priority is silently ignored,[],[],0,In the documentation is clearly stated that negative priority can be set. [""Note that it is perfectly valid to choose negative priorities for tasks that should have less priority than default.""](http://luigi.readthedocs.org/en/latest/api_overview.html#task-priority). However, the negative priority is silently ignored and reset to the default value, probably due to [this code](https://github.com/alsa/luigi/blob/master/luigi/scheduler.py#L469-L480).",{},{}

